query:
INSERT INTO installments (contractId, propertyId, installmentNumber, dueDate, amount, type, status, paidDate, paidAmount)
SELECT 
  id as contractId,
  propertyId,
  0 as installmentNumber,
  contractDate as dueDate,
  CAST(downPayment AS DECIMAL(15,2)) as amount,
  'DOWN_PAYMENT' as type,
  'PAID' as status,
  contractDate as paidDate,
  CAST(downPayment AS DECIMAL(15,2)) as paidAmount
FROM contracts
WHERE downPayment IS NOT NULL AND downPayment != '0';
